profile:
All North Overhead Doors is a garage door specialist for residential, commercial, agricultural and industrial applications, proudly serving “All North”, including Sault Ste-Marie, Espanola, Thessalon, Elliot Lake, Wawa, Chapleau, Marathon, Blind River, and more. We would love for you to contact us, our team can give you personalized advice in purchasing a garage door, an installation that meets the highest industry standards, and unequaled after-sales service thanks to our maintenance and repair program.

Our full range of products also includes electric garage door openers as well as many other accessories to go with your garage door. Think of us when it comes to buying, installing or repairing any type of residential garage door.

We have employees ready to give you the fastest service in the industry. We are located at 1131 Peoples Rd, Sault Ste-Marie, ON and are open Monday to Friday from 8 AM to 4:30 PM.

I invite you to contact us today, and on behalf of our entire team, I thank you for considering our company.

profile:
SOO Overhead Doors Inc is a garage door specialist for residential, commercial, agricultural and industrial applications, proudly serving the Sault-Ste-Marie area. We would love for you to visit us at 1695 Trunk Road. There, our team can give you personalized advice in purchasing a garage door, an installation that meets the highest industry standards, and unequalled after-sales service thanks to our maintenance and repair program. 

Our full range of products also includes electric garage door openers as well as many other accessories to go with your garage door. Think of us when it comes to buying, installing or repairing any type of garage door. 

We have four employees ready to give you the fastest service in the industry. We are located at 1695 Trunk Road and are open Monday to Friday from 8:00 AM to 4:30 PM and Saturday by appointment. 

We invite you to come and visit us, and on behalf of our entire team, we thank you for considering our company. 

André Frenette, Owner at SOO Overhead Door

André Frenette & John Karenen
Owners
SOO Overhead Doors Inc
